4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence. This course is designed for professionals who want to learn how to apply AI in different industries and roles. It is a 6-week program that covers various topics including generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The course consists of 2 live online classes per week and has a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required to enroll in this course. For more information, visit their website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop